the 2010 Census and part

00:44:32.100 --> 00:44:35.490
of the state legislature's
duty was

00:44:35.490 --> 00:44:37.090
to draw congressional districts.

00:44:37.090 --> 00:44:39.890
I had was in the
minority, and I had no say

00:44:39.890 --> 00:44:43.200
in how my congressional district
was actually drawn of the time,

00:44:43.200 --> 00:44:46.910
but it was fascinating to me,
the tools that were available

00:44:46.910 --> 00:44:50.250
in 2012, to take data by
precincts and start --

00:44:50.250 --> 00:44:54.150
