And well, yes and no.

01:14:28.950 --> 01:14:32.250
And it's important to
understand a little bit

01:14:32.250 --> 01:14:34.300
about why this came to be.

01:14:34.300 --> 01:14:39.230
So, I got to start in the
old days, back in 1992,

01:14:39.230 --> 01:14:45.540
with the dawn of ArcView 1.0,
