science standards,

02:06:54.930 --> 02:06:57.890
as well is ISTE is the
International Society

02:06:57.890 --> 02:06:59.310
for Technology and Education.

02:06:59.310 --> 02:07:02.140
So, there is that conversation.

02:07:02.140 --> 02:07:06.090
Where the confluence of that
meets, it definitely comes

02:07:06.090 --> 02:07:11.310
down to, in a lot of ways, comes
down to the individual states

02:07:11.310 --> 02:07:13.640
and then rolling out
through the district.

02:07:13.640 --> 02:07:15.890
So, I just wanted to throw
that in there, but we do work

02:07:15.890 --> 02:07:18.740
with those groups,
